        "text": "Heat a nonstick skillet over medium heat and add the frying fat. Crack eggs into the skillet and cook to your preference: sunny-side up (cover and cook until whites set) or over-easy/medium (flip once and cook briefly). Season eggs with remaining salt and pepper.",
